# Frontend API Configuration
# The frontend now uses relative paths for all API calls (/api)
# This works seamlessly in both development and production:
#
# Development:
#   - Vite dev server runs on http://localhost:5173
#   - Vite proxy redirects /api, /glogin, /accounts, /admin and /api-auth
#     requests to http://localhost:8000
#   - Optional override: VITE_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:8000
#
# Production:
#   - Frontend deployed at https://scopio.in
#   - Nginx routing handles backend paths
#
# Optional local override:
# VITE_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:8000
FRONTEND_URL=https://scopio.in
BACKEND_URL=https://scopio.in
SITE_DOMAIN=scopio.in